                <note rend="inline" type="source">710.Consultation (2)/254a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Cabot</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-07-10T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 10, 1940—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>54. A United Press item from Guatemala City states that the German Minister has
                    criticised by note to the Guatemalan Government the forthcoming meeting of
                    Foreign Ministers at Habana. Please investigate discreetly and report by
                    telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
